# process()

**Instance Method**

Request to initiate processing background upload jobs.

## Declaration

```swift
func process() -> PHBackgroundResourceUploadProcessingResult
```

## Return Value

A result type of [doc://com.apple.photokit/documentation/Photos/PHBackgroundResourceUploadProcessingResult] based on the state of the processing task.
